description: This is the main stadium in Olympic Road (Jamsil-dong), Songpa-gu, Seoul. Construction began in November 1977 and was completed in September 1984. At the same time, the stadium is also a good place for citizens to exercise and relax. In addition, the Jamsil Olympic Sports Complex often hosts large-scale events such as concerts and competitions.

address: INSPIRE Arena, 127, Konghangmunhwa-ro, Incheon, Jung-gu, South Korea
Jiha77, Haneul-gil, Gangseo-gu, Seoul 07505 South Korea
